From Deepak Chhabra Subject Re Goalie masks In article Valerie Hammerl writes and I'll give Fuhr's new one an honourable mention although I haven't seen it closely yet it looked good from a distance This is the new Buffalo one the second since he's been with the Sabres I recall a price tag of over just for the paint job on that mask and a total price of almost Yeah it's the second And I believe that price I've been trying to get a good look at it on the Bruin Sabre telecasts and wow does it ever look Whoever did that paint job knew what they were And given Fuhr's play since he got it I bet the Bruins are wishing he didn't have it